            <section>
               <id root="39b24da4-74ae-4df9-9c5e-eeffa8dc9bc0"/>
               <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
               <title>INGREDIENTS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of Benzo-Jel™ 20% benzocaine gel contains between 180-220 mg benzocaine USP, in a water soluble base of PEG 3350 USP, PEG 400 USP, flavor, Sodium Saccharin USP, and FD&amp;C Green #5.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20150501"/>
            </section>
